Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.35,0:01:49.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Time's up!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.92,0:01:54.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I studied when I was\nin the other dimension.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.96,0:01:58.59,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}And despite Inuyasha's complaints,\NI came back here.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.87,0:02:02.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,How'd it go?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.50,0:02:05.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Terrible.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.54,0:02:10.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey! Hey!\NWasn't today's test easy?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.81,0:02:12.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,D-Don't say that!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.20,0:02:38.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Say... Kagome...\NHow's your guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.94,0:02:40.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,- Guy?\N- Yeah, right!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.97,0:02:42.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The delinquent!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.87,0:02:44.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He's not a delinquent.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.28,0:02:45.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The two-timing one!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.91,0:02:48.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,H-He's not actually two-timing...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.48,0:02:51.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Then how would you\ndescribe him?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.22,0:02:54.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Err... pla... tonic?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.52,0:02:55.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Platonic?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.32,0:02:58.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He's a platonic two-timer?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.69,0:03:00.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't say that!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.73,0:03:03.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But Kagome...\NI've been meaning to tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.00,0:03:04.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.03,0:03:06.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He's no good for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.56,0:03:07.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I agree!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.40,0:03:09.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What's with you guys?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.04,0:03:11.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He's no good. Bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.70,0:03:12.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Is he really?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.37,0:03:14.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.14,0:03:17.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He's spoiled and rough, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.41,0:03:18.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Well... Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.44,0:03:21.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And jealous, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.88,0:03:24.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Say, does he know about Hojo?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.72,0:03:28.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Well... I don't think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.19,0:03:31.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Then who is he jealous about?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.19,0:03:33.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Maybe Koga.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.63,0:03:34.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Koga?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.50,0:03:40.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,There's nothing between me\nand Koga! Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.87,0:03:43.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Then why's he so jealous?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.17,0:03:48.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Well... Because Koga said he's\nin love with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.24,0:03:51.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome, are you two-timing, too?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.08,0:03:54.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.51,0:03:58.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I don't feel anything for Koga...\NI don't like or dislike him.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.75,0:04:03.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I didn't have a clue...\NThat you're so popular outside of school.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.96,0:04:07.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm not. It's all one-sided\non Koga's part.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.39,0:04:10.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,One-sided, maybe.\NBut he declared his love.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.80,0:04:14.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I wish someone would tell\nme he loves me!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.37,0:04:20.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm in... love with you!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.87,0:04:25.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's so wonderful, Kagome!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.41,0:04:27.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Well, I guess it's nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.91,0:04:31.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Actually, I've been asked\nto bear a child, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.35,0:04:34.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,By whom?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.49,0:04:36.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Koga? Or the delinquent one?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.59,0:04:38.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Neither.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.09,0:04:42.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,- A third guy?!\N- Huh? Who?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.26,0:04:45.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It HAS to be an older man\nwho'd ask such a thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.83,0:04:49.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Well, naturally. But I think\nhe already has someone he likes.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.67,0:04:51.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,- It's illicit then?!\N- Don't get involved, Kagome!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.97,0:04:53.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.14,0:04:56.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He goes around saying that\nto every young woman he meets.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.44,0:04:57.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What do you mean?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.52,0:05:07.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Please bear my child.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.16,0:05:12.65,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,C'mon! It means nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.36,0:05:20.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But, Kagome... How do you meet\nthese guys, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.53,0:05:23.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yeah! Even this current guy seems\nlike a delinquent.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.64,0:05:26.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And this Koga guy seems\npretty pushy, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.27,0:05:28.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hojo doesn't have a chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.64,0:05:31.94,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I guess you like the strong type,\nhuh Kagome?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.24,0:05:35.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's not that! It just happens...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.15,0:05:37.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,l just know you're going to\nhave problems with men!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.78,0:05:39.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,She'll be unhappy\nin marriage!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.39,0:05:42.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't say such things!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.95,0:05:45.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And how's it going lately\nwith your delinquent honey?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.86,0:05:47.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh? What'd you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.73,0:05:48.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Things going smoothly\nwith him?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.46,0:05:54.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Well... There's been...\NNo particular problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.00,0:05:56.40,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So it's going well.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.47,0:05:58.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,She must like him, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.64,0:06:00.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Let's change the subject.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.67,0:06:02.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We shouldn't have worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.37,0:06:04.81,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'll say.\NJust go about your business.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.34,0:06:07.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But it's working out and\nthat's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.39,0:06:14.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yo!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.22,0:06:20.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I wonder...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.43,0:06:28.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,82 on my arithmetic test!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.73,0:06:30.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You studied hard, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.37,0:06:33.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sis! 82!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.37,0:06:35.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I heard! Good job!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.24,0:06:38.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What're you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.68,0:06:42.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Next time, go for a perfect score!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.01,0:06:44.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Y-You're choking me!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.12,0:06:46.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Okay, settle down.\NTime for dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.75,0:06:47.48,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.19,0:06:48.91,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.89,0:06:50.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Thank you for the food.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.76,0:06:56.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Mmmm... Yummy!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.76,0:06:59.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You DO eat when you're\non the other side, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.16,0:07:01.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Veggies and mountain roots.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.27,0:07:03.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But nothing like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.44,0:07:06.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Then eat your fill.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.84,0:07:08.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,When are you going back?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.71,0:07:12.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,My test is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.98,0:07:16.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'll get a good night's sleep\nand go to class tomorrow again.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.28,0:07:18.51,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Maybe after that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.15,0:07:22.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,How'd you do on your test?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.32,0:07:24.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't even ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.99,0:07:29.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Can't be helped.\NYou've got a lot to handle.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.26,0:07:34.32,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This is heaven!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.30,0:07:38.86,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Simply heaven...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.34,0:07:41.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Divine!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.24,0:07:46.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I wonder how everyone's doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.61,0:07:49.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.08,0:07:52.07,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Divine!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.93,0:08:06.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's lonely without Kagome.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.83,0:08:10.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Think so?\NI don't notice anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.77,0:08:12.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Liar! I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.44,0:08:15.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You go into a daze\nonce in a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.04,0:08:20.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're really missing Kagome.\NOww! Hey! What're you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.91,0:08:24.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,When did Kagome say\nshe's returning?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.65,0:08:25.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.05,0:08:29.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,One... two... three...\NTomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.79,0:08:32.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,She's coming back tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.76,0:08:36.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We'd better go back to the village\nand be there to greet her!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.13,0:08:40.83,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But we've been here and there...\nwith no success.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.33,0:08:46.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Without Kagome, we can't get any\nleads on the Sacred Jewel.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.14,0:08:49.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And there was no sign\nof Naraku either.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.58,0:08:54.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If only I had a scent of him,\NI'd get on his track immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.60,0:09:19.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Want to come out?\NThen I'll let you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.98,0:09:34.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Who was that?\NMy younger brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.42,0:09:39.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He's different from you all.\NLet's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.40,0:09:54.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey, Boss!\NWhich village will be hit next?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.01,0:09:57.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Someplace with lots of\nwomen and {\i1}sake!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.14,0:10:00.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sounds great!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.95,0:10:03.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh? What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.72,0:10:06.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Boss, come over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.58,0:10:07.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.02,0:10:11.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.69,0:10:12.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.03,0:10:16.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Creepy thing!\NKill it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.13,0:10:23.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh?! A hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.17,0:10:30.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What is he?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.24,0:10:34.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,H-He... hasn't got a face!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.73,0:10:50.25,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Who am I?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.93,0:10:57.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Are you sure, Inuyasha?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.34,0:11:01.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Who can mistake this scent?!\NThis way!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.37,0:11:06.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It reeks of Naraku!\NNaraku and the smell of human blood!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.86,0:11:20.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,They've been slaughtered.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.99,0:11:22.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,They're bandits...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.50,0:11:25.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,H-His!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.63,0:11:27.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.00,0:11:31.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,His face has been carved out!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.20,0:11:33.00,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This one, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.10,0:11:33.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.94,0:11:35.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This one, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.28,0:11:41.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Every one of them...\nall without faces.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.38,0:11:44.44,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,How frightening!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.42,0:11:48.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This isn't normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.92,0:11:50.11,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's Naraku's doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.62,0:11:53.15,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But why their faces?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.55,0:12:19.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Are you the source of evil,\nspecter?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.86,0:12:26.38,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What?! He's faceless!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.52,0:12:27.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Master Muso...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.69,0:12:29.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Stay back.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.23,0:12:30.75,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.43,0:12:34.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Specter... where are you from?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.40,0:12:38.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Where? I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.80,0:12:41.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why have you done such a\ncruel thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.77,0:12:44.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Give me... your face.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.64,0:12:45.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,My face?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.04,0:12:48.67,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You killed people because\nyou want a face?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.75,0:12:49.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You evil specter!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.21,0:12:51.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,A face...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.22,0:12:53.27,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Master Muso!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.99,0:12:55.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Evil specters like you...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.79,0:12:57.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Must be destroyed!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.79,0:12:58.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Give!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.76,0:13:02.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.82,0:13:30.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,My face! I have a face!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.27,0:13:52.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hey, like my face?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.74,0:13:55.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Impudent! I'll slay you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.78,0:14:00.55,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Now that I have a fine face,\NI want a fine sword.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.05,0:14:03.38,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Your sword looks pretty nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.62,0:14:04.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.89,0:14:08.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes, it's a fine sword, all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.19,0:14:11.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You! Just who are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.67,0:14:52.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hah!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.34,0:14:59.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Dang! Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.25,0:15:03.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's not enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.65,0:15:06.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I want more...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.75,0:15:08.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Something more.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.87,0:15:23.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Maybe I'll go to that village next.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.34,0:15:27.43,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,{\i1}That village?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.11,0:15:31.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.12,0:15:43.05,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hold it right there!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.19,0:15:50.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh? Who are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.26,0:15:53.49,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Been looking for you, bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.68,0:16:06.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm off.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.14,0:16:08.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Bye-bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.38,0:16:09.54,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Be careful, now!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.75,0:16:10.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Do your best!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.18,0:16:12.74,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And there!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.52,0:16:16.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It never ceases to amaze me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.59,0:16:18.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why can only Sis go through?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.22,0:16:23.18,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hmm... It's Kagome's fate.\NThat's the only explanation.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.16,0:16:27.82,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Oh yes...\NI'd better go shopping,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.90,0:16:30.53,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,so I can stock up on food\nfor her when she returns.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.67,0:16:31.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'll go, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.07,0:16:33.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And so shall I.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.24,0:16:39.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Where's Naraku?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.71,0:16:40.73,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Naraku?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.91,0:16:41.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't act stupid!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.31,0:16:44.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're another one\nof his offshoots!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.78,0:16:46.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You reek with his smell!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.02,0:16:49.38,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You know about me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.85,0:16:51.88,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Say, tell me who I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.96,0:16:52.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Shaddup!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.16,0:16:57.03,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha, I think he's the one\nbehind all the killings, not Naraku.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.90,0:17:01.46,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,One thing's certain...\NHe has the same smell as Naraku.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.53,0:17:06.33,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Are you the one who killed the bandits\nand stole their faces?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.64,0:17:08.47,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yeah, I was the one.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.57,0:17:11.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But they were all so ugly,\NI couldn't use them.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.44,0:17:14.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But now this one...\nnice, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.68,0:17:16.17,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Did you steal that face, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.78,0:17:19.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yup. I wanted a handsome face.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.55,0:17:21.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And money, women...\NI wanted it all.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.09,0:17:23.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And I stole them all.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.79,0:17:26.85,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But it's not enough.\NThere's something missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.73,0:17:30.16,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Tell me... what is it I crave?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.43,0:17:31.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.43,0:17:33.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He's not joking.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.36,0:17:34.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He doesn't even know\nwho he is...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.13,0:17:37.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He's definitely unlike the\nothers Naraku has borne.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.51,0:17:47.64,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Humph! So they've come\nface to face.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.91,0:17:52.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He's the most abominable creation\nof my flesh.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.62,0:17:56.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha... for you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.59,0:17:59.39,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Now, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.92,0:18:02.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You attacked the village and\nset it afire, too?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.43,0:18:04.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.93,0:18:09.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I felt if I slaughtered some people,\NI'd remember something...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.93,0:18:11.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But it didn't work.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.30,0:18:13.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Although it was fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.70,0:18:15.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Just what are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.41,0:18:17.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I told you, I can't recall.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.74,0:18:22.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I know! How about Muso?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.65,0:18:24.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,My name's Muso.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.38,0:18:25.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's not bad, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.25,0:18:29.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's the name of the\nbonze who gave me this face.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.59,0:18:33.96,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,"Gave"? Didn't you kill him?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.16,0:18:35.79,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why that look?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.96,0:18:37.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I don't like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.56,0:18:38.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And I don't like YOU!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.36,0:18:40.26,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You know...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.43,0:18:43.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I really don't like your face.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.60,0:18:45.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Tell me, have we met before?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.07,0:18:49.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's no use talking to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.37,0:18:51.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.68,0:18:55.37,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Someone who smells exactly like\NNaraku is killing people senselessly!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.88,0:18:57.31,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You deserve to die!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.95,0:18:59.57,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Just try it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.79,0:19:04.78,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Die!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.66,0:19:10.29,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.30,0:19:14.13,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Not yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.50,0:19:19.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What's his body made of?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.07,0:19:22.20,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Like it's clay or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.85,0:19:30.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Naraku's Poison Insects!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.03,0:19:44.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,His arm!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.50,0:19:47.93,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He's absorbing the Poison Insects\ninto his body!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.43,0:19:50.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,My Wind Tunnel is useless!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.30,0:19:55.30,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,This is amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.77,0:19:57.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,So what's in that village?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.04,0:19:59.98,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What're you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.04,0:20:02.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That village is calling me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.55,0:20:04.04,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,If I slaughter the villagers,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.18,0:20:06.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,maybe THIS time,\NI'll remember something.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.45,0:20:07.71,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.39,0:20:13.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.09,0:20:18.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hmm... Pretty good!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.47,0:20:22.23,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Hiraikotsu!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.44,0:20:25.09,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,There!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.57,0:20:27.87,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He's formidable!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.37,0:20:29.70,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,We must use caution.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.77,0:20:31.97,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yes! He's made from Naraku,\nafter all.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.21,0:20:33.68,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Piece a cake!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.28,0:20:38.01,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.08,0:20:39.14,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,How's that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.68,0:20:41.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.49,0:20:44.61,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.09,0:20:46.92,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.32,0:20:48.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Inuyasha!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.63,0:20:49.28,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.53,0:20:50.72,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Sorry I'm late!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.79,0:20:52.56,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't come, Kagome!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.93,0:20:55.02,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,That woman!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.94,0:21:02.10,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What did l just feel?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.24,0:21:04.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He's an offshoot of Naraku.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.14,0:21:06.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Stay back!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.78,0:21:07.80,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Uh-huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.95,0:21:13.08,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Who is she?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.22,0:21:16.19,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Don't just stand there in a daze!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.52,0:21:17.45,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Die!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.82,0:21:19.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.72,0:21:20.66,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It's working!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.79,0:21:24.06,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What is it?\NWhat is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.83,0:21:25.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Woman?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.13,0:21:29.62,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Huh? Yeah... That woman!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.53,0:21:31.90,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What're you babbling about?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.37,0:21:33.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'll finish you off!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.54,0:21:34.63,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,The woman! Move!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.74,0:21:36.50,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Woman!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.71,0:21:37.44,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.54,0:21:40.60,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Why, that!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.45,0:21:43.38,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.55,0:21:45.41,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Run!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.72,0:21:49.38,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.79,0:21:50.34,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagome!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.32,0:21:55.35,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,You're the one!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.53,0:21:56.99,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,W-Who is he?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.76,0:21:58.75,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,What does he want?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.93,0:22:01.12,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I've wanted this... woman!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.07,0:23:50.84,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Taking us for fools!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.91,0:23:52.21,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,He was made\nfrom Naraku's flesh...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.28,0:23:53.77,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Yet he claims\nhe never heard of Naraku!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.84,0:23:56.75,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Kagura tells Inuyasha and the others\nof Muso's whereabouts.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.15,0:24:00.95,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It is the cave where fifty years ago,\NKikyo tended to the bandit Onigumo.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.12,0:24:02.24,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,It may be a trap!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.32,0:24:04.69,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,But we should find out something\nif we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:04.76,0:24:07.52,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,And during that time,\NNaraku sets out to destroy Kikyo!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.69,0:24:11.89,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,Next on Inuyasha:\N"Onigumo's Memory Restored!"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.10,0:24:15.36,Style1,Comment,0,0,0,,I'm gonna get revenge for what\nhappened fifty years ago!
